---
title: Sticky Sesame Chicken & Ginger Veggies with Garlic Rice
description: These diced chicken have everything - they’re sweet, savoury, sticky, and covered in sesame seeds! Pile them high into a cushiony bowl of fluffy rice and fragrant green veggies, and don’t miss a drop of that delicious glaze.
